Title: Tesoro PRE ICO
Body: Tesoro PRE ICO will be from 22 march till 21 april the main ico will be open after the pre ico end  To join the pre sale http://www.tesorofund.io  This is a small description about Tesoro :   ORO token will be launched by Tesoro through ERC20.  ORO is the first tokenised crypto-currency to pay their investors profit on a monthly basis. Tesoro token holders will be enabled to make equable profits without having experience or deep-rooted knowledge in the crypto-currency market. ORO was founded by experienced traders who have in-depth knowledge of both the the FOREX and Crypto-currency markets and they will ensure a return for their valued investors.  Tesoro will guarantee a return of up-to 60% of the profit. The remaining 40% of the profit within the fund will be reinvested to guarantee the longevity of the token and maximise profit for investors.  Profits will be paid to the investor in ethereum in the 15th of every month.  When investing in ORO, investors are exposed to more opportunities to maximise profits, as ORO prides itself on a varied portfolio which minimises risk. Our diversified portfolio will trade using the top 20 Cryptos and currencies that are currently circulating on the market.  When the ICO finishes, the token will be listed on the exchange market.
